<center>
<h1>Renew Password</h1>
</center>

<div class="row mx-2">
パスワードを変更します.ユーザー名と新しいパスワードを入力してください.<br>
</div>

<div class="mx-auto" style="width: 300px;">
<form action="/newpass" method="post">
<div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1">Username</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="uname" maxlength="40" placeholder="user">
  </div>
<div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1">New Password</label>
    <input type="password" class="form-control" maxlength="40" name="pass1" >
  </div>
<div class="form-group">
    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1">New Password Again</label>
    <input type="password" class="form-control" maxlength="40" name="pass2">
  </div>
  <br>

<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Renew</button>
<button type="reset" class="btn btn-danger">Reset</button>
</form>
<a class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="/login" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
Login
</a>
<br>
<a class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="/createaccount" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
Create Account
</a>
</div>
